---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Brodin Vance — math student, game developer, and occasional cook based in Waterloo, Ontario."
>
  <div class="wrap">
    <section class="about">
      <div class="head">
        <h1>About</h1>
      </div>

      <p>
        I&rsquo;m working toward building quantum technology &mdash; somewhere near space,
        communication, and sensing. I don&rsquo;t have the product yet; I have a direction
        and a habit of building things until the direction sharpens.
      </p>

      <p class="muted">
        Right now that means a math degree at Waterloo, a quantum-mechanics self-study track,
        and a steady stream of side projects across software, games, and the occasional kitchen
        experiment. This site is the logbook.
      </p>

      <div class="links">
        <a href="https://github.com/BrodinVance">GitHub</a>
        <a href="mailto:brodin.c.vance@gmail.com">Email</a>
        <a href="/writing">Read the latest &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 3.4rem 0 5rem;
    max-width: var(--measure);
  }

  .head {
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
  }

  p.muted {
    color: var(--ink-dim);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .links {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1.4rem;
  }

  .links a {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    color: var(--ink-dim);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding-bottom: 0.15rem;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .links a:hover,
  .links a:focus-visible {
    color: var(--accent);
    border-color: var(--accent-dim);
  }

  .links a:focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
    outline-offset: 3px;
    border-radius: 1px;
  }
</style>
